<A>__{the magellan has arrived. lv 426 is a gray moon shrouded in clouds. behind it looms its father planet epsilon, a lurid gas giant banded in red and gold, half swallowed in darkness. the magellan dives into a forced orbit around lv 426: rockets firing continually, nose pointed down. telescopes, sensors and antennae sprout once more from its hull.}
